# rClimateIndex


R code for  data extraction from  climatic data obtained form http://www.esrl.noaa.gov/psd/thredds/catalog/Datasets/catalog.html.

Data are used for italian seasonal forecast and concerning many index related to asian moonsoon activity and sea surface temperature state in mediterranean area.

Weather type classification are done by using software developed in http://cost733.met.no/   action.

See details in http://cost733.geo.uni-augsburg.de/cgi/cost733plot.cgi 


Correlation matrix function are also provided by using pressure (pp), mean air temperature ( tg), and rainfall form E-OBS dataset.( http://www.ecad.eu/download/ensembles/download.php) from Ensembles project.
